<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, tun wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der künig, mit grossem volk <add>von Ungern
