<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der kunig, daz sich das volk auf dem perg
                                <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>awsz</expan>
<expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> solt, mitsampt <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
